sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev
    participant CI
    participant Reg as Registry
    participant Deploy

    rect rgb(255,245,245)
    Note over Dev,Deploy: Before mitigation
    Dev->>CI: Workflow uses action@v1
    CI->>Reg: Build + push unsigned artifact
    Deploy->>Reg: Pull artifact
    Deploy-->>Deploy: Deploy without provenance check
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over Dev,Deploy: After mitigation
    Dev->>CI: Workflow uses action@<commit SHA>
    CI->>CI: Policy gate validates workflow + permissions
    CI->>Reg: Push signed artifact + attestation
    Deploy->>Reg: Pull artifact
    Deploy->>Deploy: Verify signature/provenance
    Deploy-->>Deploy: Deploy only if valid
    end
